{"tid":1906714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人民日報刊登《總書記來過我的家》，被武漢人批評為甚麼不來武漢看看？","createTime":"2020-03-02T06:14:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T10:46:43.000Z","uid":155095,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0146691d54f3e8cbf638a60451b8a95a129ba5eb","tid":1906714,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T06:14:45.000Z","msg":"武漢還在水深火熱，北京為慶祝勝利做鋪墊的『大國戰&ldquo;疫&rdquo;』好像突然&ldquo;下架了&rdquo;，真的？人民日報卻在繼續刊載『習近平來到我們家』，有自稱武漢網民的質疑，&ldquo;別說來到我們家了，就到我們武漢看看行嗎？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/eb9115dc-5b99-11ea-94fe-005056a964fe/w:1240/p:16x9/HK0301-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.rfi.fr%2Fmedia%2Fdisplay%2Feb9115dc-5b99-11ea-94fe-005056a964fe%2Fw%3A1240%2Fp%3A16x9%2FHK0301-2.jpg&h=afed5c1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n『總書記來過我的家』 好啊 &nbsp;為什麼不去武漢？<br />\n<br />\n中共中央機關報『人民日報』1月初開始，不定期在頭版重要位置刊載『總書記來過我的家』系列宣傳文章，最新一篇『總書記來過我的家 好日子又上新台階』刊載在『人民日報』3月1日頭版。文章記敘農民尤桂蘭見習近平的經歷：&rdquo;22歲那年進京受到毛澤東主席接見，82歲又在自家見到習近平總書記，尤桂蘭常說自己這輩子&lsquo;值&rsquo;。總書記來時，家裡150畝地，一條漁船，一年收入有8萬元，日子過得像蜜一樣甜&ldquo;<br />\n<br />\n最新一篇是3月2日刊出的『總書記來過我的家 美好家園樂融融』，說的是習近平去年7月15日在內蒙古赤峰市馬鞍山村考察，進到四世同堂的村民張國利家&rdquo;&ldquo;問寒問暖&rdquo;，&ldquo;總書記說，新中國成立70年來，老百姓生活芝麻開花節節高。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ntdtv.com/assets/uploads/2020/03/4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ntdtv.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F4.jpg&h=cd6a79d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n『人民日報』的目的是要宣傳一個親民、英明的領袖形象，本台香港特約記者甄樹基報道，人民日報頭版有些時候甚至對武漢爆發的疫情隻字不提，也要為歌頌習近平的『總書記來過我的家』系列宣傳文章騰出顯眼位置。<br />\n<br />\n的確，『總書記來過我的家』連續發表的這一階段正是從當局隱瞞疫情，到疫情全面爆發，武漢人到現在還沒有擺脫苦難的階段，但文章散發的氣息絲毫跟人民正在感受的無關。<br />\n<br />\n有網友評論，&ldquo;疫情還沒有過去，武漢人更是水深火熱，『總書記來過我們家』讓人看着刺眼，遠離現實，總書記真的那麼好？為什麼不去武漢看看？他害怕什麼？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n有人問，&ldquo;宣傳部是不是搞錯了時間？&rdquo;"},{"pid":"efcaacbc182c331491fd880bc0f2b82fd78f6ab4","tid":1906714,"uid":155095,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T08:30:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images1.epochhk.com/pictures/140654/phpBYriPZ@1200x1200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages1.epochhk.com%2Fpictures%2F140654%2FphpBYriPZ%401200x1200.jpg&h=f9e75e23&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0fb9874d7f3f1f92cb2727544830e081ae2b5790","tid":1906714,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T10:06:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/L7WRePD-cGc/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FL7WRePD-cGc%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=7ba5e9d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/MPA4fjbuQ1k/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FMPA4fjbuQ1k%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=e87304fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8be97f5944352d392756d0d0c9f97bc91d8cec19","tid":1906714,"uid":158457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T10:55:35.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;別說來到我們家了，就到我們武漢看看行嗎？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n對習總指手劃腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c17d514840a80347fadf09d3b0af09b729fa6afa","tid":1906714,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T12:00:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecdf01a39e55bfdcb4d2484a3d9b9c92a93bc170","tid":1906714,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T10:50:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df830197c7cd31d7df829f6fc1f014debe0d6e06","tid":1906714,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T09:55:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"86369def0987e4cb15c78f2f578d2e7c9236ca8a","tid":1906714,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T09:58:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec41b9d5ad84fa025d481c6b611dca1c75052f8d","tid":1906714,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T10:12:48.000Z","msg":"老衲來我家，清潔齊參加"},{"pid":"90ba6e96d546852c296e49fb9cbc64afdc042f45","tid":1906714,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T14:18:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e4072a58a153985b6688132dad520e8c061cf27","tid":1906714,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T04:12:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c46ec7703d88963dd79b100a09dd62333b25abd2","tid":1906714,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T04:14:26.000Z","msg":"習近平：會死 不了"},{"pid":"e2e68458c920aa620fcaa56c2e299f74a045fc6e","tid":1906714,"uid":59408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T04:17:06.000Z","msg":"感恩總書記<br />\n感恩共產黨<br />\n聽黨話<br />\n跟黨走 <br />\n<br />\n加速，加速！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"981600ada867596e615002322366337c417f4680","tid":1906714,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c46ec7703d88963dd79b100a09dd62333b25abd2","tid":1906714,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T04:14:26.000Z","msg":"習近平：會死 不了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T04:17:15.000Z","msg":"岩岩話去羅喎"},{"pid":"d1ff8e33d41a6618d4e43e156cd0f4161f0f17b1","tid":1906714,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T10:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"904d40c7fd4946a41681cd715176990d8e818ee8","tid":1906714,"uid":95519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T10:46:43.000Z","msg":"把武漢給我屠一屠"}]}